invite drawing.

create window canvas. # creates a window, and names it in the program and also the window title canvas
make canvas dimensions 400 by 400. # changes the window size, eventually implement a thing where you can type like pixel art type dimensions eg 16 by 16 but then say 16 by 16 scale 4 and then it scales it 4x

make canvas at 200 by 200 black. # makes pixel at 200x 200 black
